Ok, 可以係Google Chrome 上用一個叫 UI Vision 的Extension, 然後用我一段超簡單的 macro script 來一蚊一蚊咁交稅。<br />
<br />
Step 1:<br />
1. 開Chrome, URL 入 <code>chrome://extensions/</code>, search &quot;UI.Vision&quot;<br />
<img src="https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTDU6R7nwu3kEMGcyj6RRo1gfn63Nm72ALbc4JxsQn3g8?filename=7o1wCVH.png" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7o1wCVH.png&h=19933dc5&s={SIZE}" /> <br />
2. 裝完之後，係Chrome登入 <a href="http://ppshk.com" data-sr-url="https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fppshk.com&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIj9kuezr8BQg8uGmIe3q97E%3D&h=0ff5f1c1" data-auto-link target="_blank">ppshk.com</a><br />
3. 做你平時用PPS交稅的步驟，加入交稅賬單等等，一直去到呢一頁<br />
<img src="https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeVktQYzbXmLUsKfuhNPUmNg12nXUeK6kjukouZhoNBqN?filename=B18fkaK.png" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB18fkaK.png&h=eeb7136a&s={SIZE}" /> <br />
4. 跟著，用你個Chrome右上角藍色的U字icon開 UI.Vision extension<br />
<img src="https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZr1ufoMybKd3Rqtx8xq82dFQ4gFh4aKk2tKxSvM5TkwH?filename=dEuihYM.png" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEuihYM.png&h=24d9a480&s={SIZE}" /> <br />
5. 用 &quot;+Marco&quot; 起個script, 求其叫&quot;pps'<br />
<img src="https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVoYvuoSRnCwNMR4YfJi9oYsUvhSwWnMRAEjxfQoUVeQx?filename=Rbp2KGg.png" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbp2KGg.png&h=d22294f1&s={SIZE}" /><br />
6. Paste 呢段野落去<br />
<pre><code data-type="">{
  &quot;Name&quot;: &quot;PPS tax&quot;,
  &quot;CreationDate&quot;: &quot;2019-10-9&quot;,
  &quot;Commands&quot;: [
    {
      &quot;Command&quot;: &quot;clickAndWait&quot;,
      &quot;Target&quot;: &quot;name=Pay10xxx&quot;,
      &quot;Value&quot;: &quot;&quot;
    },
    {
      &quot;Command&quot;: &quot;click&quot;,
      &quot;Target&quot;: &quot;name=BILLTYPE&quot;,
      &quot;Value&quot;: &quot;&quot;
    },
    {
      &quot;Command&quot;: &quot;select&quot;,
      &quot;Target&quot;: &quot;name=BILLTYPE&quot;,
      &quot;Value&quot;: &quot;label=1-Tax&quot;
    },
    {
      &quot;Command&quot;: &quot;click&quot;,
      &quot;Target&quot;: &quot;name=AMOUNT&quot;,
      &quot;Value&quot;: &quot;&quot;
    },
    {
      &quot;Command&quot;: &quot;type&quot;,
      &quot;Target&quot;: &quot;name=AMOUNT&quot;,
      &quot;Value&quot;: &quot;1&quot;
    },
    {
      &quot;Command&quot;: &quot;clickAndWait&quot;,
      &quot;Target&quot;: &quot;name=proceedBut&quot;,
      &quot;Value&quot;: &quot;&quot;
    },
    {
      &quot;Command&quot;: &quot;clickAndWait&quot;,
      &quot;Target&quot;: &quot;id=Image11&quot;,
      &quot;Value&quot;: &quot;&quot;
    },
    {
      &quot;Command&quot;: &quot;click&quot;,
      &quot;Target&quot;: &quot;id=Image12&quot;,
      &quot;Value&quot;: &quot;&quot;
    }
  ]
}</code></pre><br />
7. 將 <code>Pay10xxx</code> 的<code>xxx</code>改成你個bill number, 如<code>Pay109196898999A</code><br />
8. Save, 完成！你可以試試 Play Marco:<br />
<img src="https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNorTWHVCLEMRk9vT9nkeetbT4jkuqTYC4DxTQGdaVaLJ?filename=VX37bon.png" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVX37bon.png&h=552c4a2b&s={SIZE}" /> <br />
<span class="red">9. （注意！如果你個PPS已經timeout, 唔該登入再去番步驟3果一頁。個Macro 一定係要由呢頁開始先識郁）</span><br />
10. Macro 運作成功俾到一蚊既話，就可以用play loop, 例如100次:<br />
<img src="https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRfuTsgxMA2qcKgqMM3mHAgPacmkSQ7XgnPC79s5kPWbB?filename=GU5pX4q.png" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGU5pX4q.png&h=d3beb01e&s={SIZE}" /> <br />
<br />
Optional: 方便下一次用，你可以right click, save as bookmark:<br />
<img src="https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfVV7UsmR1GpJQ72CcCydqhb8HFpXAUozvChAges3Luvv?filename=z5SWPb9.png" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5SWPb9.png&h=414eac43&s={SIZE}" /><br />
 咁以後登入PPS去到步驟3果頁，按bookmark link，就可以逐蚊逐蚊咁交稅！個畫面跳下跳下，幾治癒架！<br />
<br />
<br />
以上步驟唔好似好難，但你想想，花少少時間搞掂之後，你就識多樣野之餘，又可以盡公民責任交足稅，又慳番狂㩒PPS交稅既時間，你話幾好！<br />
<br />
大家加油！<img src="/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif" class="hkgmoji" /><img src="/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif" class="hkgmoji" />

